Uganda project

RNA data from paxgene blood tubes

counts <- read.csv(file="norm_counts_paxgene_121422.csv", header=T, check.names=FALSE, row.names=1)
coldata <- read.table(file="coldata_paxgene_121422.txt", header=T, row.names=1)
coldata$Status= factor(coldata$Status, levels=c("Case", "Control"))
counts <- counts[ ,match(rownames(coldata),colnames(counts))]

ultra_data_all<- SummarizedExperiment(assays=list(counts=as.matrix(counts[1:81,])), colData = coldata)

ultra_data_all <- mkAssay(ultra_data_all, log = TRUE, counts_to_CPM = TRUE)
assays(ultra_data_all)
## List of length 4
## names(4): counts cpm log_counts log_cpm

get signature scores

#siglist_nano <- names(TBsignatures)

ssgsea_result <- runTBsigProfiler(input = ultra_data_all,
                                  useAssay = "log_cpm",
                                  signatures = TBsignatures_nanostring,
                                  algorithm = "ssGSEA",
                                  combineSigAndAlgorithm = TRUE,
                                  parallel.sz = 1)

g2 <- signatureBoxplot(inputData = ssgsea_result,
                     name = "Boxplots [ssGSEA]",
                     signatureColNames = names(TBsignatures_nanostring),
                     annotationColName = "Status", rotateLabels = FALSE)

plot(g2)

Simple Heatmap

counts <- read.csv(file="log_cpm_paxgene_march2023_noHG.csv", header=T, check.names=FALSE, row.names=1)
coldata <- read.table(file="coldata_paxgene_march2023.txt", header=T, row.names=1)

mat = as.matrix(counts)
mat = t (scale(t(mat)))

###this worked

df=data.frame(Status=coldata$Status, HIV_status=coldata$HIV.stage, Ultra_result=coldata$Xpert.Ultra)

col_fun = colorRamp2(c(-4, 0, 4), c("blue", "white", "red"))
col_fun(seq(-4, 4))
## [1] "#0000FFFF" "#7E52FFFF" "#B38BFFFF" "#DCC4FFFF" "#FFFFFFFF" "#FFCFBFFF"
## [7] "#FF9E81FF" "#FF6846FF" "#FF0000FF"
ha = HeatmapAnnotation(df = df, col = list(Status=c("Case" ="red",  "Control" ="#3333FF"), HIV_status=c("stage_1"="#CC99FF", "stage_2"="#99CCFF", "stage_3"="#3399CC"), Ultra_result=c("MTB_positive_high" = "#339900" , "MTB_positive_medium"="#FFCC33", "MTB_positive_low"="#00CC99", "MTB_positive_verylow"="#66CC00", "Negative"="#999999")), simple_anno_size = unit(0.7, "cm"))

Heatmap(mat, name="Scaled score", col=col_fun, show_row_names = T, show_column_names = T, top_annotation = ha, show_row_dend = F, column_dend_height = unit(3, "cm"), column_names_side = "top", row_names_gp = gpar(fontsize=7), column_names_gp = gpar(fontsize=10))

Pheatmap code

annotation_col = data.frame(
  Group=coldata$Status,
  HIV_status=coldata$HIV.stage,
  Ultra_result=coldata$Xpert.Ultra)

ann_colors = list(
    Group=c(Control = "#7570B3", Case = "#E7298A"),
    HIV_status = c(stage_1="#33CCFF", stage_2="#9900FF", stage_3="#FF0000"),
    Ultra_result = c(MTB_positive_high = "#CC0000" , MTB_positive_medium="#FF9999", MTB_positive_low="#99CCFF", MTB_positive_verylow="#66CC00", Negative="#999999"))

pheatmap(mat, annotation_col = annotation_col, 
    annotation_colors = ann_colors)
